{"tid":1776401,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我娛樂台牙喪遇到好事了...18+","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T07:30:37.000Z","uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"32e2e0f0b1b32f8dadc0a47943af891c0ea5f1c3","tid":1776401,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"頭先！！我牙喪！！<br />\n坐506巴士冇錢比！！！！<br />\n很驚！！因為冇錢比就代表要含車長的撚！！！！<br />\n我想跑下車...但車長即刻關了門！！想我含他的撚！！<br />\n突然！！有個女仔借了5蚊比我！！<br />\n仲話唔洗還！！<br />\n我牙喪哭左！！很感動！！<br />\n我愛上那個女仔了！！想和她HH<br />\n如題...18+<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s965Fz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs965Fz8.jpg&h=4174c75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgQunO2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgQunO2.gif&h=d7d11116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"688771cc6637378b178bf030a0dc45de439032d1","tid":1776401,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"同佢做愛一次要收幾錢‧‧‧"},{"pid":"460cd637c71fc53056acbcce743faf3dd1e521af","tid":1776401,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c393b7c397737ea6d63c507b6ef53bbaedf740a","tid":1776401,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"屌牙權對奶射精在她鎖骨"},{"pid":"d866e18ebc7d0ddabb53b3c1b1d84718c9ca0ee9","tid":1776401,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"唔洗還比我 唔想同你有任何瓜葛"},{"pid":"0da3811c0efc618eeff9f7bdb03c06c166c604b1","tid":1776401,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"上次似yerin的女生？"},{"pid":"1ba392686327300fd678c9e0389431d6a1da53e9","tid":1776401,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:40:44.000